g.text: 3.1: updates the order status to "delivered" and informs operation success
2.1: shows the list of orders of the customer with the "delivered by carrier" status and asks to select one
1.1: shows the list of orders of the customer that have not
been marked as "delivered" and asks if he/she wants to
mark any of those orders as delivered
1: wants to view/check the status of their open orders
